<li><a href="http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,501020902-344136,00.html" class="external text" title="http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,501020902-344136,00.html" rel="nofollow">"Ascent of the Fireflies"</a>, TIME about Tome Torihama called "Kamikaze Mom"</li>
<li><a href="http://www.chiran1945.jp/" class="external text" title="http://www.chiran1945.jp/" rel="nofollow">TOEI movie "I will die only for you above all"</a> (Orewa Kimi no tamenikoso Shiniyuku / 俺は、君のためにこそ死ににいく) about Tome Torihama ("Kamikaze Mom"), the Chiran high school girls and young Army kamikaze pilots flying Ki-43 Hayabusa fighters, <a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/switch-language/product/B000TLYCSG?language=en%5FJP," class="external text" title="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/switch-language/product/B000TLYCSG?language=en%5FJP," rel="nofollow">DVD</a> (2007)</li>
<li><a href="http://ww2db.com/other.php?other_id=18" class="external text" title="http://ww2db.com/other.php?other_id=18" rel="nofollow">WW2DB: Kamikaze Doctrine</a></li>
</ul>
